<title>Occurrence Labels</title>
<context IDD_OCCURRENCE ID_EDIT_OCCURRENCELABELS />

Occurrence labels can be attached to a repeating item or a repeating roster by right-clicking on the dictionary element and selecting <b>Occurrence Labels</b>. Alternatively, that option can be found on the <b>Edit</b> menu. To edit an occurrence label, simply click on the appropriate row and add the label.

<center><image occurrence_labels.png /></center>

Occurrence labels can be used as <link drag_option_menu.csdoc>row labels in a roster</link>, in <link getocclabel_function.csdoc>programmed logic</link>, or as replacement text in the <link create_fills_in_questions.csdoc>CAPI text window</link>.
